xjavax.tv.service.navigation

Class SIElementFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • xjavax.tv.service.navigation.ServiceFilter
      • xjavax.tv.service.navigation.SIElementFilter

  • public final class SIElementFilter
extends ServiceFilter
    SIElementFilter represents a ServiceFilter based on a particular SIElement (such as a TransportStream or ProgramEvent). A ServiceList resulting from this filter will include only Service objects with one or more corresponding ServiceDetails, sd, such that:
    • sd is contained by the specified SIElement, or
    • sd contains the specified SIElement
    -- according to the type of SIElement provided. Note that no guarantee is made that every SIElement type is supported for filtering. ServiceList
